Here dubugging can also be done like a true debugging experiance.
Vs code has different extensions, which user can instal according to their wish.
There are also n number of shortcuts in vs code,which will help us to code faster.
Under extensions we have many like,
         Sublime text keymap and setting controller.
         Settings sync
         Prettier
         Bookmarks
         Cloak
         CSS peak
         DotENV
         Editorconfig
like this we have n number of extensions in vs code.
All programming languages like c,c++,java,javascript,html and etc can be done here.
This vs code helps us with syntax highlighting,bracket matching,snippets and etc.
